  <mainContent><![CDATA[<h2>Course Overview</h2>
<p>This course is ideal if you are interested in how our democratic law-making system and how the English legal system works.</p>
<p>This course provides you with the knowledge to pursue the study of Law to Higher Education and will assist those who wish to enter employment in a related field.</p>]]></mainContent>
